<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Kodexplorer on 蓝惠の小窝</title><link>//www.lanhui.live/tags/kodexplorer/</link><description>Recent content in Kodexplorer on 蓝惠の小窝</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>蓝惠の小窝</copyright><lastBuildDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2020 22:09:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="//www.lanhui.live/tags/kodexplorer/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>可道云添加新磁盘</title><link>//www.lanhui.live/p/1050/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2020 22:09:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>//www.lanhui.live/p/1050/</guid><description>&lt;p>注意：这是基于windows宝塔面板操作&lt;/p>
&lt;p>在宝塔中搜索php.ini文件打开&lt;/p>
&lt;p>搜索
;open_basedir =
在后面加上你要加的添加的磁盘路径(windows系统为例)&lt;/p>
&lt;p>如
;open_basedir =;open_basedir = C:;E:&lt;br>
过个磁盘用;隔开&lt;/p>
&lt;p>如果不管用试试取消防跨站攻击。参考&lt;a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/guohong-hu/p/9350076.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">evanwoo&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>